@carlosmarcialt is one of the most inspiring Artist and Human Being we have met and we feel incredibly lucky to count him among our Advisors 🙏

This is probably the most important meeting of our whole NFT journey.

Not only he understood instantly our mission but he also  helped us to structure our long-term vision.

A 2-hour meeting with @carlosmarcialt is worth more than 6 months of hardcore strategic planning.

But we definitely got his attention. He gave us his email and told us that he was in Paris for a few days so we could arrange a proper meeting.
